node.text:
Sunsets in Santorini 🌅 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting explorerfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @explorerfervor 

Tag a friend who you’d escape to Greece with!

Loved for its one of a kind architecture and beach views, this Greek town will take your breath away. If you’re visiting Santorini this summer, don’t forget to hike to the town’s volcano and unwind at a winery afterwards ☀️🍷

📷 @cbezerraphotos & @_letstravel_
📍 Santorini, Greece

The world’s biggest cat 🦁Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @explorerfervor 

It’ s a hybrid offspring of a male lion and a female tiger. It has parents in the same genus but of different species. Distinct from the similar hybrid tigon, and is the largest of all known extant felines. 🐾

📽 @docantle w/ @kodyantle
